title: S13 Ep116: Supernatural News/Parashare: Episode 181

description: BEYOND the DARKNESS is back to report Supernatural News from around the world and share YOUR Paranormal emails & phone calls! plus, while Dave is away this week, Tim has recruited the one and only, Mallie Fox to fill in!  It's a strange week of stories with a Killer Clown on the loose, Post Malone believes he is under a paranormal curse, and there's a fire shooting out of that hole, and it burns! PLUS we answer your calls & emails in our ParaShare segment.
